{
  "stem": "1753.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I've got one child with her, a little girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have three wonderful sons that work with me in my company and very astute and very hard working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I am very proud of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their names-- the oldest is Jordan, then comes Steven, then comes David.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My little girl's name-- little?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She is now 15 going on 16.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name is Suzy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm the proud grandfather of six wonderful grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All my sons are married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I could come back for just a short period in 200 years from now, and incidentally, I intend to come back in 200 years just for a short little while to see how things are.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time, I'm going to be a butterfly then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that-- that's OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I still will be able to talk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would tell them [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to really make it a point and familiarize themselves what happened 200 years earlier, to the world, and the miscellaneous nations of the world, and in particular, the Jews that suffered and how proud all of them came-- became after the establishment of the Jewish nation, Israel.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would say that's probably the most wonderful thing that happened to the Jews of the world because as long as there's an Israel, every Jew whether they lives in Argentina, in the Soviet Union, in Ethiopia, South America, or the Far East-- wherever they live-- or the United States, they are looked up to with respect that unfortunately, we did not have when we did not have a homeland.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't go anywhere, could we then?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now there is an Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
